Class TableCalculated

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.pschatzmann.common.table.TableCalculated
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITable<java.lang.Number>, ITableEx<java.lang.Number>, java.io.Serializable

    public class TableCalculated
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITableEx<java.lang.Number>
    Table which supports calculated columns which are specified with a formula. We use the javascript scripting engine to evaluate the formula. The Column names are used as variable names.
